                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Camden NJ US America<ptr target="loc.03836_n1"/></name>
                    <date when="1887-07-23">July 23 '87</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>Y'rs of July 8 (?)<ptr target="loc.03836_n2"/> rec'd&#8212;with A's<ptr
                target="loc.05908_n1"/> note on fourth page. All goes safely with me so far
                thro' the long fearfully hot spell here &#8212;It is clouded over a little to
                day&#8212;, &#8212;some relief&#8212;I have no news to write you ab't my affairs or
                self. I sit in the big chair by the open window as I write this&#8212;"the same
                subject continued"&#8212;Best prayers &amp; love to you all, Mary<ptr
                target="loc.02189_n1"/>, Alys &amp; little
                R</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc_jc.00187_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
        </body>
